thread.title: Patrick Kinsley

author: Patrick Kinsley
title: Patrick Kinsley
text: We purchased 200 customized usb's for our school district (graduation gift with the graduating class's slideshow). We worked with Elliot Portnoy and he worked very quickly and even let us know about a sale we could take advantage of. Our order was placed quickly and we received the order just after a week of finalizing the specs. Excellent service, super fast delivery, excellent quality. Our logo came out great on the flash drives. Thank you!
